sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as KServe Gateway /<br/>kube-rbac-proxy<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant REST as MLServer REST<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant gRPC as MLServer gRPC<br/>8081/TCP gRPC (HTTP/2)
    participant DataPlane as DataPlane<br/>V2 Protocol Handler
    participant Registry as Model Registry
    participant Allowlist as Trusted Runtimes<br/>Allowlist
    participant Model as MLModel Runtime<br/>(sklearn/xgboost/lightgbm/onnx)
    participant Pool as InferencePool<br/>(multiprocessing workers)
    participant Metrics as Metrics Server<br/>8082/TCP HTTP
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    participant Kafka as Kafka Broker<br/>9092/TCP
    participant KafkaSrv as MLServer KafkaServer
    participant OTel as OpenTelemetry<br/>Collector

    Note over Client,Gateway: Flow 1: REST Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>REST: HTTP/8080 (pod-internal)<br/>No encryption
    REST->>DataPlane: infer(payload)
    DataPlane->>Registry: get_model(name)
    Registry->>Allowlist: validate implementation
    Allowlist-->>Registry: allowed
    DataPlane->>Model: predict(request)
    Model-->>DataPlane: InferenceResponse
    DataPlane-->>REST: response
    REST-->>Gateway: JSON Response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,Gateway: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: ModelInfer RPC<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>gRPC: gRPC/8081 (pod-internal)<br/>No encryption
    gRPC->>DataPlane: infer(payload)
    DataPlane->>Pool: dispatch (parallel mode)
    Pool->>Model: predict(request) [worker process]
    Model-->>Pool: InferenceResponse
    Pool-->>DataPlane: response
    DataPlane-->>gRPC: response
    gRPC-->>Gateway: gRPC Response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS/gRPC Response

    Note over Kafka,KafkaSrv: Flow 3: Kafka Event-Driven Inference
    Kafka->>KafkaSrv: consume message<br/>TCP/9092
    KafkaSrv->>DataPlane: infer(payload)
    DataPlane->>Model: predict(request)
    Model-->>DataPlane: InferenceResponse
    DataPlane-->>KafkaSrv: response
    KafkaSrv->>Kafka: produce response<br/>TCP/9092

    Note over Prometheus,Metrics: Flow 4: Metrics Scraping
    Prometheus->>Metrics: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8082
    Metrics-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics<br/>(counters, histograms)

    Note over REST,OTel: Flow 5: Distributed Tracing (Optional)
    REST->>OTel: OTLP spans export<br/>gRPC (insecure)
    gRPC->>OTel: OTLP spans export<br/>gRPC (insecure)
